servinfo.title: Air Cleaner Filter Inspection and Cleaning

ptxt.intxrefpoff: Air Cleaner Filter Removal and Installation:For M16A Engine with VVT

servinfosub.title: Inspection
servinfosub.ptxt: Check air cleaner filter for dirt. Replace excessive dirty filter.

servinfosub.title: Cleaning
servinfosub.ptxt: Blow off dust by compressed air from air outlet side of element.
